<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c2">( ... - ١٢٠٤ هـ)</span> <span class="c2">( ... - ١٧٩٠ م)</span> محمد <span class="c2">(أبو عبد الله)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>محدث، مؤرخ،<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
